text:
Tindal se to sayad hi koi jaanta hoga tujhe but singh se to tu poore campus me famous tha wo senior ho yaa koi junior bas singh bolna hai samajh aa jaani thi ki baat kiski ho rahi ğŸ¤©
Bhai itna jyada hai tere baare me ki kaha se shuru karu kaha khatam karu kuch pta nahi chal rha bs Zindagi bhar ke liye jo nishaan tune diya hai wo har din dekh ke yaad aayegi teri ğŸ¤• ğŸ˜‚ 
Ek akela bhai jiske saath meri jamne lagi thi reason btane ki jarurat nahi haiğŸš­ Bhai shuru se last tak bina tere room gaye hue maja hi nahi aata tha aur wo alag baat hai 10 me se 2 baari tu room pe milta tha.Bhai tere karan mai kitne logo se mil paaya aur saare tere dost dost nhi bhai jaise lagte theğŸ¤©ğŸ¤© . Bhai kitne tripod ka hissa hain humlog tumhe ache se yaad hoga. Kya mast rahti thi apni aaj bahar jaana hai to jaana hai kah kar wo chaahe endsem ki night ho yaa normal night ho mast Nightout maar ke aate the aur wo Nightout nahi memories hai jo mai college ke baad sayad kabhi na kar paaun waisa kyunki tumlog ke jaisa milna mushkil hi nahi naamumkin hai ğŸ˜. And I am lucky to have you in my life broğŸ¤©ğŸ˜
Aur meri gpl ke time tu eklauta tha jiske laat se mujhe sabse jyada dar aata rahi thi aur mai pahle to khush tha ki tu available nahi hai but fr aate hi Jo kohraam machaya tune wo poora ka poora time rewind ho rha mere aankho ke saamne kaise mere saamne naach kar laat chla rahe the ğŸ˜¤ Lucky tu bhi maan apne aap ko ki mai tere koi bhi birthday pe nahi tha gpl ke timeğŸ˜„ But rahta bhi to raham kar deta kyunki humesha mareej jo ban jaata tha tu. Tere alawa sayad hi hoga koi insaan campus me jo start ke har college fest me bimaar pad ke hospital me admit hota tha aur uske karan hume bhi rahna padta thağŸ˜„ aur tera fever ka kyahi kahna ğŸ™„
Aur sayad wahi wajah thi ki itne jyada log tujhpe girte the aur tinder match ka to koi comparison hi nahi haiğŸ˜„
Bhai jaldi hi milte hain bhai yaha kyahi aur kitna hi likhi sab kam hai tere liye to. Bas jaldi milke ek trip karte hain bakchod wala jisme sabhi wapas se mile aur haan yaad karna band mat karna mujhe nahi to Hyderabad se Bangalore aate hue der nahi lagegi mujhe ğŸ˜œğŸ˜
Love u veereâ¤ï¸

text: Tune jitni proud feel karwayi hai apne baap(mai) ko ki koi bhi bete ne nahi di hai itni khushi.Tu dost yaa bhai nahi balki beta hai tu mera aur Apne bete pe kon memoir likhta hai unse to bonding banti hai janmo janmo tak. Dekhte dekhte tu amrendra se Bahubali ban gya aur fir yahi Bahubali har jagah hahakaar macha ke rakh diya.Yaad hai mujhe maine apna 1st day jab wing me introduction karwaya tab tak tumlog sabhi aapas me mil chuke the tabhi mai mila tumlogo se aur wo room bhi ache se yaad hai, us room ko pariameya kah sakte ho jaha pe tumlog sabhi ne jamawda laga rakha tha aur wahi tune Abhay ki li thi tabhi samjh gya tha tu bakchod londa hai. Aur wahi se pta bhi chla ki tu mera bhai bhi hai aur saare culture tab tak mai miss kar chuka tha to samjhaane wala tuhi thağŸ¤©. Tab se leke jo aaj tak ki bonding hai wo bonding nahi memories me badalti chali gayi.1st year me bakchodi kari 2nd year me cc aur Library ke chakkar kaate aur teri cycle leke bhaag jaata tha jisse tu Pareshaan hota tha and fr 3rd year me aero coordi aur 4th year me time kha mila full bakchodi karne ki. Mai manate rah gya ki tu apne birthday pe mere hathe na chadh jayiyo kyunki jo kaam tumne, Anshuman aur MM(mohit ma******d) ne kari thi wo mai kabhi zindagi bhar nahi bhulunga aur yaad rakhunga aur jab kabhi mauka milega tumlogo ki gaand nahi kch aur todunga ğŸ˜ so prepared rahna pahle se hi. And abhi naa aane ke liye sorry yaar bt mai thora critical condition me phash gya tha tab nahi aa paaya pta hai kon bhoshdike hai jisne ye rumour falai bt mai naam disclose nahi uski kah ke lunga uski memoir me jaake original reason padhna udhar.Wese maine bhi bahut jyada miss kiya bhai excited mai bhi bahut jyada tha tabhi gya tha gate ka paper dene aur ruk gya tha udhar 1 mahine tak tumlogo se milne ke liye bahut logo se mila bhi bt tum 2nd group me aaye the to tab tak nikal chuka tha mai but mjhe apni saari saath ki bakchodi yaad hai poster se leke wo mohit ke room ki dj night(jisko permanent bar kah sakte the apan) wha tak ki journey bahut ache se yaad hai aur kabhi nahi bhulne jaa rha ye sab bakchodi. Aur bakchodi ke saath saath tune help bhi bahut kri hai wo bhi ache se yaad rahegi mujhe wo mth se leke placement ki alag alag pdf bhej kar help karna wo bhi nahi bhulunga mai. Beta bas ek word nahi emotions hai mere liye usi ko bolta hu ya sunta hu jisse dil se dil tak ki har jagah bonding banti hai.Love u lot bhai mujhe 4 saal (2.5 yearsğŸ˜”) jhelne ke liye.I hope ki humlog jaldi mile aur wahi bakchod bar ke jaisa mahaul ho jha humlog wapas se mile. Aur tumhari kya kisi ki pic nahi lagai hai maine kyunki mujhe maloom nahi tha ki isme kaisa photos lagayi jaati hai tabhi bas apni lga di kisi se aisa koi dushmani nahi thi meri. Baaki yaad karte rahna nahi to mera kyaa hai chaar gaali start me sunake mai to yaad karunga hi karunga kyunki baap jo hu terağŸ¤©ğŸ˜‚. Words aur memories to khatam nahi hote bt feelings bahut hai ye bas samjh jaa tu. Bas safe rahna bete aur 25 ke speed se nahi kamse kam ijjat rakhne ke liye baap ki 70-80 ki chalaya kar ğŸ¤­ğŸ˜‚.

Saare moments yaar yaad karke kya mast vibe aati hai aur lagta hai kyun hi khatam hui humari college life ğŸ˜”Kaash ye jo 1.5 yrs almost corona ne le liya sayad isme aur bhi jyada bakchodiyaan hoti but nahi mil paaya hume mauka to jitna pal ya bitaya hua usko kabhi bhool nahi sakti khaash karke wo pubg ki class btana na pade ki humne PUBG101 laaya tha apne clg life me ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ yaa fr jha baithte the hum teeno me se koi ek bhi miss hota tha to poora class missing lagti thi hume aur to aur exam me kuch dikhaaye ya nahi tu bt hume dara ke jarur rakhta tha ki jaise kitna hi likh rha ho alag baat hai last me marks thora hi upar niche rahta tha bt teri writing confidence ko salute karta hu kuch nahi aate hue bhi poora ka poora copy bharna koi tujhse seekhe ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ Sach bataun to galiyaaya karte the humlog exam ke baad bt fr marks aane ke baad asliyat pta chal jaati  thi hume aur fluid mechanics iska jeeta jaagta example hai ğŸ˜œğŸ˜„ğŸ˜„ Bhai wo last to last summer to bhool hi nahi sakte humlog kyunki tere nautanki ke bina koi bhi aisa din nahi jaata tha jisse fr bore hoke humlog hi tereko pareshaan karne aa jaate the aur to aur gate pe ek word likhe the yaad to hoga hi (r***)ğŸ˜œğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ Jisse tu fr baad me chidhne bhi lga tha tab aur maje aate the chidhaane me. Bhai bhai saare moments hi memories ke roop me yaad rahenge bahut kam logo ke saath memories banti hai bt unme se tu bhi ek hai ğŸ¤—â˜ºï¸
Aur haan jab kabhi mauka mile to jarur yaad karna warna mai saare raaz disclose kar dunga wo nickname se leke kiske peeche bhaagta tha aur abhi kis wajah se bzy chal rha sab kch pta hai mujhe teri to next time bahana mat maarna aur milne jarur aana ğŸ˜Š Bhai likhna to khatam ho nahi hota hai jitna memories hai in chaar saalo me bas yaad rakhiyo sabhi ke sabhi jaise likhte hue mujhe saare revise ho rahe waise hi padhte hue tujhe hona chahiye ğŸ™„ğŸ¤ª Aur jaldi hi milte hainğŸ¤—

So agar mai college se 4 saal me pass ho rha hu to usme sabse bada haath tera hai.Wo shuru se TA ki drawings bana ke dena aur to aur TA ke endsem me bhi risk leke help karna ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚.Aisa aisa kitna courses hai jisme maje se humara CHE KE BAKCHOD LAUNDE ka group poora ka poora tere pe depend rahta tha aur tu humari naiyaa paar lagata tha ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚.Ye sab ke liye jitna thanks bol lu kam padega tere liye ğŸ˜ŠğŸ¤—. 
Ab aate hain bina courses ke masti kitni kari hai wo to count bhi nahi kiye jaate hain.Bas itna samjh le ki jitna Nightout maarna aur IIT gate pe jaake khaana khajana banana koi tujhse seekhe ğŸ˜‚ Soch ke hi muh me paani aa jaata hai mereğŸ¤¤â˜ºï¸. text: Be bhoshdike bete yaad aa jaani chahiye saari baat agar mai bas memories ka naam lu to tere se itna to expect kar hi sakta hu jitna tu close ho gya hai mere aur pta hi hai aalsi bhi utna hi hu to bahut kam likhunga bt samjh jaana bas jo chutiyaapa failaaya hai tune use sahi kar. Mai to ab bas Kaash ban ke rah gya ki Kaash mai wha hota to aisa nahi hone deta but sach bataun to mai dar ke nahi aana chaha udhar kyunki mai bahut bada daldal me phansh jaata kyunki dono hi taraf mere jigri dost the aur mai agar wha hota to beech me pis jaata aur poora happiness barbaad ho jaata tabhi maine decide kiya tha ki naa jaau aur to aur bahana bhi mil gya tha paiso wala aur kismat bhi thori saath de di ki wha se nikla to alag alag trip bhi ban gaye dosto ke sath to mai to naahi to regret kar sakta naahi blame kar sakta bas last ki jo kch memories banani thi clg me usme saath nahi de paaya baaki tujhe bhi pta hai ki kon sa aisa din nahi rha tha clg me jisme apan log ne masti ya bakchodi naa kari ho. Aur mujhe aaj bhi yaad hai pahli baar sabse achi bonding tujhse hi hui thi aur fr aaj tak wo kabhi tooti nahi balki alag alag memories hi create karte rahe kitno ko yaad Karu tinder se leke summer room partner se leke ye placement (yaha thori shikayat thi) but fr usse nikal ke wo achanak se fr se milna kanpur Central pe aur kahte hain na achi bonding jaha ho jaati hai wha plan nahi karni padti plan khud humare liye work karti hai aur fr wha bhi 1 month ke upar rahe wha start me to masti kari humlogo ne bt baad me tune mood ki maa bahan karna start kari tumne bt fr sambhaal hi liya tha samajh aur fr se wahi masti kayam rahi apni. Aur haan placement ki shikayat ye hai ki tune jab se placement ki preparation se leke placement lag jaane tak to full confidence dilata rha aur sach batau to thora dar se bhi padh liya karta tha ki ye cse ka hai to kch bhi puch sakta hai to start jab coding se kari thi to achi chal rahi thi and ki bhi achi mehnat thi hum teeno ne but jab meri hui thi aur tujhe btaya tha to ik Teri nahi lagi thi us time bt meri khushi me tu khush to nahi tha bas ye shikayat rahi tujhse ğŸ˜¡. But jaise hi hui teri mujhe yaad hai tune tab jaake ache se congratulations bola tha mjhe ğŸ¤©ğŸ¤©. So thanks for all memories which we have created ğŸ¤— wo chaahe cricket se leke bandi tak ki ho sab me aise jagah pe partner tu hi tha aur bas tu aage miliyo to pahle waale Mohit mc se milu aisa feel karwana nahi to udhar hi is baar band bahana start karunga teri ğŸ˜Š.
